<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Further Sketcher improvements ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* It is now possible to directly use external geometry as input for tools like offset or transform (array), for both external construction and defining geometry. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17615 Pull request #17615]
* External geometry (projected or intersecting) is now by default real (defining) geometry (which does not need to be traced as in 1.0 and prior). It can be toggled to construction geometry as any other geometry [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17736 Pull request #17736]
* The Sketcher axes are now displayed with infinite length. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17312 Pull request #17312]
* Sketches are now ordered alphabetically in the [[Image:Sketcher_MapSketch.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_MapSketch|Attach sketch]] dialog. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/16518 Pull request #16518]
* Group dragging was added, making it possible to drag all the selected geometrical entities. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18273 Pull request #18273]
* There is a new preference that, if checked, makes external geometry creation independent of the current construction mode - it is always created as reference geometry in such a case. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18697 Pull request #18697]
* A preference was added to allow optional grouping of the [[Image:Sketcher_CreateLine.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreateLine|Line]] and [[Image:Sketcher_CreatePolyline.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreatePolyline|Polyline]] tools. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20165 Pull request #20165]
* When selecting a constraint or a geometry element within the sketch, the corresponding Tasks panel list is now automatically scrolled to that object. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18859 Pull request #18859] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20866 Pull request #20866]
* Status bar hints were added for Sketcher geometry creation, constraint, edit and transform tools. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21632 Pull request #21632],  [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21751 Pull request #21751], [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21806 Pull request #21806] and [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21840 Pull request #21840]
* Sketches are now automatically scaled after entering the first dimension to avoid breaking the shape when the first dimension is much larger/smaller than the current size of the geometry. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21084 Pull request #21084]
* When creating geometry the mouse movement is ignored if a value is entered in the [[Sketcher_Workbench#On-View-Parameters|on-view-parameters]] (OVP). Tab cycles between OVP input boxes and Enter now confirms. Deleting the value of an OVP input box enables mouse movement for the dimension again. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/20925 Pull request #20925]
* Rendering of geometry lines is now prioritized over constraints so that dimensions lines don't cover the geometry. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21982 Pull request #21982]
* Now all parts of dimension constraints can be selected, not only labels. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21920 Pull request #21920]
* It is now possible to use the Ctrl+A shortcut (or Select All option in the Edit menu) to select all geometries within the sketch. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23289 Pull request #23289]
* Box selection from left to right now uses another color than from right to left to indicate different behavior. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23261 Pull request #23261]
* There is a new preference for constraint symbol size. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23366 Pull request #23366]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Spreadsheet Workbench ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Default shortcuts for [[Image:Spreadsheet_StyleBold.svg|24px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleBold|Bold text]], [[Image:Spreadsheet_StyleItalic.svg|24px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleItalic|Italic text]] and [[Image:Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline.svg|24px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline|Underline text]] have been added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/15556 Pull request #15556]
* Double-clicking on the separator in the header now resizes the column to content. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/16296 Pull request #16296]
* Zoom was added to Spreadsheet. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/16130 Pull request #16130]
* Icons were added to context menu entries. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22773 Pull request #22773]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Surface Workbench ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* A task panel was added for the [[Image:Surface_BlendCurve.svg|24px]] [[Surface_BlendCurve|Blend Curve]] tool. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21825 Pull request #21825]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== TechDraw Workbench ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Image:TechDraw_AreaDimension.svg|24px]] [[TechDraw_AreaDimension|Insert Area Annotation]] tool now properly accounts for holes in faces. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17740 Pull request #17740]
* Shape validation is now available and can be enabled in [[TechDraw_Preferences#Advanced|Preferences]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18282 Pull request #18282]
* Scaling of SVG symbols has been fixed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18757 Pull request #18757]
* New ''r'' format specifier was added. It rounds the dimension value to the step specified as decimal before ''r''. For example, ''%0.5r'' (or just ''%.5r'') rounds to 0.5. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19393 Pull request #19393]
* Snapping of detail view highlights to the closest vertex in the TaskDialog drag highlight process was added. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22036 Pull request #22036]
* Instead of [[TechDraw_ToggleFrame|toggling view frames]], they are now shown and hidden automatically when hovering the cursor over the view. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22869 Pull request #22869]
* The cosmetic circle commands were renamed and grouped for clarity. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22945 Pull request #22945]
* The deprecated [[Image:TechDraw_LandmarkDimension.svg|24px]] [[TechDraw_LandmarkDimension|LandmarkDimension]] and [[Image:TechDraw_LinkDimension.svg|24px]] [[TechDraw_LinkDimension|LinkDimension]] tools were removed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21483 Pull request #21483]
* Number of decimals and reference dimension options were added to the [[Image:TechDraw_Dimension.svg|24px]] [[TechDraw_Dimension|dimension]] task panel. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23501 Pull request #23501]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Import and Export ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The DXF importer was significantly redesigned at the implementation and user level for a more predictable and consistent user experience. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22251 Pull Request #22251]
* The DXF importer gained improved support for BLOCK and INSERT DXF entities. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22045 Pull Request #22045]
* The DXF importer now reports import stats after an import. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/21985 Pull Request #21985]
* The alignment of sketches in SVG export and legacy DXF export has been fixed. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/19765 Pull request #19765]
</div>


